LOL. My dh and I "try" to go out on Saturday nights. Sometimes the kids
stay with my MIL, other times they go to a drop in child care center. If we
don't go to a movie, we end spending the whole time talking about the kids,
too! So, I'm trying really really hard not to. But, when your life is your
kids . . . actually I think he'd rather talk about the kids than about my
latest crochet project.

Carron
